@startuml
title Update Profile - Clean Architecture Sequence
hide footbox
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor Researcher
boundary UpdateProfileView
control UpdateProfileController
participant UpdateProfileInputBoundary <<boundary>>
control UpdateProfileInteractor
participant UpdateProfileDataAccessInterface <<boundary>>
entity ServerRepository
collections "ScholarMatch API" as Server
participant UpdateProfileOutputBoundary <<boundary>>
control UpdateProfilePresenter
entity UpdateProfileViewModel

Researcher -> UpdateProfileView: Edit fields and choose Save
UpdateProfileView -> UpdateProfileController: execute(form values)
UpdateProfileController -> UpdateProfileInputBoundary: execute(inputData)
UpdateProfileInputBoundary -> UpdateProfileInteractor: execute(inputData)
UpdateProfileInteractor -> UpdateProfileDataAccessInterface: updateProfile(profile)
UpdateProfileDataAccessInterface -> ServerRepository: updateProfile(profile)
ServerRepository -> Server: PUT /api/profile
Server --> ServerRepository: saved profile JSON
ServerRepository --> UpdateProfileInteractor: User
UpdateProfileInteractor -> UpdateProfileOutputBoundary: prepareSuccessView(outputData)
UpdateProfileOutputBoundary -> UpdateProfilePresenter: prepareSuccessView(outputData)
UpdateProfilePresenter -> UpdateProfileViewModel: setProfile(profile)
UpdateProfileViewModel --> UpdateProfileView: notify change
UpdateProfileView --> Researcher: Show saved profile

alt Request fails
    Server --> ServerRepository: error response
    ServerRepository --> UpdateProfileInteractor: DataAccessException
    UpdateProfileInteractor -> UpdateProfileOutputBoundary: prepareFailView(message)
    UpdateProfileOutputBoundary -> UpdateProfilePresenter: prepareFailView(message)
    UpdateProfilePresenter -> UpdateProfileViewModel: setError(message)
    UpdateProfileViewModel --> UpdateProfileView: notify change
    UpdateProfileView --> Researcher: Show error
end
@enduml
